                            <comment id="15393814" author="carlyeks" created="Tue, 26 Jul 2016 13:51:15 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fix looks good, the failure in the trunk dtests hopefully isn&apos;t related, but I kicked off another run just to be sure.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15395316" author="slebresne" created="Wed, 27 Jul 2016 09:40:55 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;That trunk dtest failure didn&apos;t reproduce in the new run, nor did it reproduce for me locally over a few runs of that test. The fix is also simple enough that I have some confidence in saying that it&apos;s very unlikely to create new problems. So committed, thanks.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
